//! shipped 9 new reduction ops (logsumexp, argmax/argmin, std/var,
//! any/all/count_nonzero, amin_dim/amax_dim, prod_dim) and 13 runner
//! arms. Generated by acto-critic audit.
//!
//! Upstream pin: PyTorch 2.11.0+cu130 / `/home/doll/pytorch` tree.
//! Source files this audit opened:
//!
//!   - aten/src/ATen/native/ReduceOps.cpp:1512-1559 (logsumexp_out_impl)
//!   - aten/src/ATen/native/ReduceOps.cpp:1775-1823 (argmax/argmin impl)
//!   - aten/src/ATen/native/ReduceOps.cpp:2085-2108 (var/std)
//!   - aten/src/ATen/native/ReduceOps.cpp:1758-1772 (amin/amax_out)
//!   - aten/src/ATen/native/ReduceOps.cpp:1681 / :1667 (any/all)
